==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rorulent
<hw>Ro"ru*lent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rorulentus</ets>, from <ets>ros</ets>, <ets>roris</ets>,
dew.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Full of, or abounding in, dew.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having the surface appearing as
if dusty, or covered with fine dew.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rory</ent>⟦br⟧
